c: 42
v: 20
t: "Jwaŵele ali nkusachilila (ni itendo yakwe) malipilo ga ku Akhera, chitukan’jonjechesye pa malipilo gakwe, ni jwaŵele ali nkusachilila (ni itendo yakwe) malipilo ga pa duniya, chitumpe palakwepo (yayannembele kuti impate), ni ngasakola jwalakwejo ku Akhera liunjili lililyose (lya yambone)"